snippet.title: MOVED: Quest For Glory 4 - Shadows Of Darkness Full Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
NOTE: This video has been moved due to a channel upgrade. New video here:
https://youtu.be/BLMm3h6Q1gw?list=PLFD5C527CF20D625E

The full length (other QFG4 trailers are missing the flyby intro) high quality trailer (no compression prior to YouTube) for 'Quest For Glory IV - Shadows Of Darkness' by Lori and Corey Cole at Sierra On-Line.

This is a non-playable demo released to the public in 1993 recorded using Hypercam, DosBox & General Midi.

http://webspace.webring.com/people/ed/d_blakeley/Games/QFGSeries/QFGSeriesIndex.html - QFG Fan page with information, pictures, demos, walkthroughs, and maps.

NOTE: This video has been moved due to a channel upgrade. Old video here:
https://youtu.be/sbJjDnhTnCs

-~-~~-~~~-~~-~-
